flowchart LR
    Mobile([Mobile<br/>adaptive GPS])
    Friend([Friend Device])
    LocSvc[Location Service]
    SubSvc[Subscription Service<br/>ACL + radius filter]
    LocCache[(Latest Location<br/>in-memory cache TTL 5m)]
    History[(Wide-Column Store<br/>history, opt-in)]
    Bus[(Pub-Sub<br/>topic per user)]

    Mobile -->|/location| LocSvc
    LocSvc --> LocCache
    LocSvc -.->|opt-in| History
    LocSvc -.->|publish| Bus
    Bus -.->|subscribe| SubSvc
    SubSvc -.->|WS push| Friend

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Mobile,Friend external
    class LocSvc,SubSvc service
    class LocCache,History,Bus store
